# Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored). Vite reads it over `.env.development`.
#
# Default dev URL is http://127.0.0.1:8000 — only works if uvicorn runs on this PC.
# To use your droplet API from localhost instead:
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-api-host.example.com
#
# After changing, restart: npm run dev
